== Tanaramt n uziweɣ s imsaddasen inegniyen ==
[[Tugna:Mercury transit 1.jpg|thumb|Annay n wezray n uziweɣ (Azag aberkan s ddaw n wammas n tugna) ma d azag yellan ɣef tama tazelmaṭ n tegra tanadukt d [[azmul anafuk]]]]
Annay anezwaru yakk i uziweɣ s [[amsaddas|umsaddas]] yella-d deg [[tasut tis 17|tsut tis 17]] sɣuṛ n umesnallun [[Galileo Galilei]] anda i yerra tamawt ɣer [[annuf amtiwgan|wannuf amtiwgan]] ass mi i d-yuni [[tatrit]] maca amsaddas-is ur yelli ara d win igedṛen i wakken ad iwali annuf n uziweɣ. Ma d [[Pierre Gassendi]] ixdem-d deg useggas n [[1631]] yiwen n umsaddas s waci i yezmer ad yani yis [[Tukkit (tasnallunt)|azray]] n umtiweg zdat n tafukt. Ma deg useggas n [[1639]] yessaweṭ [[Giovanni Battista Zupi]] ad yani w ad isnirem d akken aziweɣ ila (yesɛa) annufen imezzayen yettemcabin agla n tettit d wayyur, dɣa tamawt-a tessentem-d tuzzya n uziweɣ ɣef tfukt.<ref name=strom/>

Yiwen seg inelfuyen imesnallanen imidrusen iga d [[adrag]], anda iderreg uziweɣ d tetrit yiwet n tikkelt yal kra n tsutin. Dɣa annay amyiwen  i wnelfuy-a yella-d deg wass n [[28 mayyu]] [[1737]] ass mi i d-tt-yuni umusnaw [[John Bevis]] deg [[asanay ageldan n Greenwich|usanay ageldan n Greenwich]]. Ma d adrag i d-iteddun yezmer ad yili deg wass n [[3 dujamber]] aseggas n [[2133]].<ref>{{Tanagit s wedlis
